- Vanilla JS ES modules, no bundler, CDN WebLLM, multi-file layout — exact same pattern as the plan
- Reuse the `import("https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@mlc-ai/web-llm@0.2.84/+esm")` dynamic import idiom
